<HEADLINE> Missy Elliot Talks To Spin Magazine </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Missy ``Misdemeanor'' Elliott is a devout  
Baptist who goes to church, but her raps often include raunchy 
behavior and foul language. The rapper/producer is feeling a little 
conflicted. 
</P>
<P>
	``I go through battles where I'm like, `Dag, I'm still cussing  
on albums, and I don't wanna cuss no more,''' she said in July's 
Spin magazine. 
</P>
<P>
