-- I won't drink and I don't smoke. But I don't want people to be 
like, `Okay, now she's Reverend Elliott.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Elliott's new record, ``Da Real World,'' is her follow to her  
multi-platinum 1997 debut, ``Supa Dupa Fly.'' Besides her own solo 
career, she is also a top producer and songwriter. 
  	   	
