<HEADLINE> Big Movers in the Stock Market  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks that are moving substantially or trading  
heavily today on the New York Stock Exchange, American Stock 
Exchange and Nasdaq Stock Market. 

</P>
<P>
 *NYSE    	

</P>
<P>
 *British Steel PLC, up 3 7/8 at 26 1/16    	
</P>
<P>
	The group confirmed it is negotiating a merger with with  
specialty steel company Koninklijke Hoogovens NV of the 
Netherlands. British Steel said it expects to make a detailed 
announcement no later than Monday. 

</P>
