	-- ``The Cobweb'' (1954).  
</P>
<P>
	-- ``Queen Bee'' (1954).  
</P>
<P>
	-- ``Hell on Frisco Bay'' (1955).  
</P>
<P>
	-- ``Rock Pretty Baby'' (1957).  
</P>
<P>
	-- ``Tammy and the Bachelor'' (1957).  
</P>
<P>
	-- ``Summer Love'' (1958).  
</P>
<P>
	-- ``Dragstrip Riot'' (1958).  
  	   	
</P>
