<HEADLINE>  First Lady Won't Say Magic Words </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Looking more like a candidate than ever, Hillary  
Rodham Clinton worked the crowd at the City College commencement 
Wednesday and cautioned graduates against those who try to ``lift 
up our public schools and the students they serve by tearing them 
