	Elsewhere in television ....  
</P>
<P>
	MOMENTS TO TREASURE: MTV celebrates the decade's most memorable  
screen moments in ``9 Movie Moments for the '90s,'' showing 10 p.m. 
EDT Wednesday. Jodie Foster, John Singleton and Samuel L. Jackson 
are among those discussing milestone scenes from films including 
``Basic Instinct,'' ``Pulp Fiction'' and ``Titanic.'' 
</P>
